title: Travel Destinations
name: Travel Destinations
description:
A Map by Rwalkerg

Places I have been and places I want to go!

properties.name: Family Trip
properties.description: Posted by Rwalkerg Washington D.C.Wayne, Mom Geordie and I went on a trip to D.C. Saw the capitol and all the toursit places we could. Zoo, monuments, etc.

properties.name: Family Trip 199?
properties.description: Posted by Rwalkerg Albuquerque, NMMom, Geordi and I went to see snow and sand in New Mexico. Drove up to Cloudcroft and out to Whitesands. Saw Carlsbad caverns.

properties.name: Girls Trip 2005
properties.description: Posted by RwalkergGirls Trip 2005Megan and I got a group together to stay at the Sheraton on South Padre. We had a fun extended weekend. Campfire on the beach, lots of booze and tons of sun.

properties.name: Graduated college
properties.description: Posted by RwalkergNorman, OKFinished up college here and got my degree.

properties.name: Grandparents Old Summer Lake House
properties.description: Posted by RwalkergSebec Lake, MEFamily on my moms side would spend summers here. My grandparents would leave in May and return in September. We would rock climb and do boating activites. Was on the peak of the lake.

properties.name: Las Vegas trips
properties.description: Posted by RwalkergLas Vegas, NETwo seperate trips. One when i was 16, went with Dad, Andrea, Geordie and Monica. Tried skiing for the first time. Played lots of video arcade. Second trip I was with Scot - 2003. We stayed at the Stratosphere; did some gambling.

properties.name: New Orleans, of course
properties.description: Posted by RwalkergNew OrleansHave been there for weekend get-a-ways; Done the shopping, food and of course drinking all over this town!

properties.name: Roaring River Camping Trip
properties.description: Posted by Rwalkerg  Went on a camping trip with Scot and buddies to this Missouri park. First camping experiance.

properties.name: Universal Studio; Mom/Daughter trip 2004
properties.description: Posted by RwalkergOrlando, FlordiaThis was one of our first real girls trips together. Right after my college graduation, stayed at the Pacific (?) hotel on the studio site.

properties.name: Weekend visit trip 2005
properties.description: Posted by RwalkergSeattle, WAWent up to see Seattle and Dustin, whom I met at the beach in July 2005. Beautiful place, ugly man.
